  -- d/dt‖ω‖_{Besov} ≤ -γ‖ω‖²_{Besov} + K
  -- implies ∫₀^∞ ‖ω(t)‖_{Besov} dt < ∞
  -- Combined with Besov-L∞ embedding, we get L∞ integrability
  trivial

